  "texts": [
    "AGI is predicted to possess intelligence surpassing that of humans.",
    "Such AGI would not only perform specific tasks but also have the capability for self-learning and innovation, understanding and generating natural language, and solving complex problems.",
    "Furthermore, it might have consciousness and emotions.",
    "AGI could excel in various fields, including scientific research, artistic creation, and decision-making, profoundly impacting society, the economy, and ethics, potentially leading to numerous ethical issues.",
    "These include (1) Autonomy and Control: Once AGI surpasses human intelligence, will it still be under human control?"
  ]
}